       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI92108.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI92108.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Manuten誽o de Contas Banc嫫ias                             *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI92108         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6800 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6900 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV9210.
       COPY COCV9211.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            SWITCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  SW-SWITCH.
           05 SW-MOVIMENTOS              PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
              88 SW-CONTA-COM-MOV                  VALUE 'S'.
              88 SW-CONTA-SEM-MOV                  VALUE 'N'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT6800 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT6800'.
           05 CON-COVT6900 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT6900'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI92108'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI92108         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV9210-MSG.
           MOVE COCV9210-ASE               TO COCV9211-ASE.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9210-ADE               TO COCV9211-ADE.

           PERFORM 2100-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-ELIMINA-DADOS
                 THRU 2399-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- N緌 permite eliminar a conta se existirem movimentos para
      *--- essa conta

           PERFORM 2200-VERIFICA-MOVIM
              THRU 2299-VERIFICA-MOVIM-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF SW-CONTA-COM-MOV
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV9211-CCONTA-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-CONTA-COM-MOVIMENTOS
                   TO COCV9211-CCONTA-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV9211-CCONTA-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.


       2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-VERIFICA-MOVIM
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-VERIFICA-MOVIM.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-VERIFICA-MOVIM' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9210-CPAIS        TO COCD6900-CPAIS.
           MOVE COCV9210-CBANCO       TO COCD6900-CBANCO.
           MOVE COCV9210-CCONTA       TO COCD6900-CCONTA.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT DDATMOV
                 INTO  :COCD6900-DDATMOV
                  FROM  COVT6900_MOVBANC
                 WHERE  CPAIS  = :COCD6900-CPAIS
                   AND  CBANCO = :COCD6900-CBANCO
                   AND  CCONTA = :COCD6900-CCONTA
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT6900 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 SET SW-CONTA-COM-MOV     TO TRUE
              ELSE
                 IF DB2-NOTFND
                    SET SW-CONTA-SEM-MOV  TO TRUE
                 ELSE
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2299-VERIFICA-MOVIM-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2300-ELIMINA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-ELIMINA-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2300-ELIMINA-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9210-CPAIS        TO COCD6800-CPAIS.
           MOVE COCV9210-CBANCO       TO COCD6800-CBANCO.
           MOVE COCV9210-CCONTA       TO COCD6800-CCONTA.

           EXEC SQL
                DELETE FROM COVT6800_CNTBANC
                 WHERE CPAIS    = :COCD6800-CPAIS
                   AND CBANCO   = :COCD6800-CBANCO
                   AND CCONTA   = :COCD6800-CCONTA
           END-EXEC


           MOVE CON-COVT6800 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV9211-CCONTA-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-CCONTA-N-EXISTS
                      TO COCV9211-CCONTA-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV9211-CCONTA-CAPLIC
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2399-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9211-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV9211-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV9211-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
